title: My life
name: My life
description:
A Map by Eabluhm

These are the places in my life that mean something to me.

properties.name: Arches National Park
properties.description: Posted by EabluhmÂ During a long trip to the west coast with two friends and my sister, this was one of a few stops. We camped for one night on top of a plateau and awoke the next morning to free roaming cows outside of the tent.

properties.name: Hidden Valley Camp
properties.description: Posted by EabluhmI spent the summer of 2005 here at this most beautiful place that I have yet to see. I had a great time here and met some really fantastic people!

properties.name: Melanie and Patrick's place
properties.description: Posted by EabluhmHome to friends Patrick and Melanie, Michelle the dog, Al the cat, and birds Sid and Pucha(?).

properties.name: My best friend's home
properties.description: Posted by Eabluhmtoms river, njI have never been there and I haven\'t seen my friend in a very long time, but I still feel very connected to this place.

properties.name: My childhood
properties.description: Posted by Eabluhm909 elm street michigan city, in 46360The place of many skinned knees, games of ditch, and watermelon eating contests!

properties.name: My first place on my own
properties.description: Posted by Eabluhm534 graham place bloomington, in 47401My first house in Bloomington, Indiana.

properties.name: My last place
properties.description: Posted by Eabluhm1440 windfield road bloomington, inAlthough this was my last place in Bloomington, I was not very unhappy to see it go. Also shared with Erin, this house was nice, but our landlord was crap!

properties.name: My second place
properties.description: Posted by Eabluhm761 sherwood hills drive bloomington, inI shared this townhouse with my sister and my friend Tanya for two years. We had a fantastic landlord and had some pretty wild times there.

properties.name: My third place
properties.description: Posted by Eabluhm739 sherwood hills drive bloomington, inAlso owned by the same fantastic landlord, this townhouse I shared with my friend Erin, my two cats, and her puppy Gracie.

properties.name: The boys house
properties.description: Posted by EabluhmAh ... many nights spent at this house playing lots of video games, playing euchre, and feeding the pet snake live rabbits. Those were the days ...

properties.name: Wild Mustang Ranch
properties.description: Posted by EabluhmWild Mustang RanchMy parents and I took a trip to South Dakota during the summer of 2004. We visited touristy sites like Mt. Rushmore and Custer State Park, but we also made time to see the Wild Mustang Ranch.
